Solaria Says Updates to Production Line to Reduce Costs 8%

-- B y   E m m a   R o s s - T h o m a s
-- 
2011-07-12T06:54:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-12/solaria-says-updates-to-production-line-to-reduce-costs-8-.html
Solaria Energia y Medio Ambiente SA (SLR) 
said it has updated it production line of high-efficiency
photovoltaic cells and the changes will bring an 8 percent
reduction in costs. It commented in an regulatory filing today
in  Madrid .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emma Ross-Thomas at 
 erossthomas@bloomberg.net  